  m_Name: NeighborJournal_03
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 12
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #3"
  category: 3
  content: "T\u1EC7 th\u1EADt, Th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 b\u1ECB phong t\u1ECFa r\u1ED3i!!
    T\xEAn \u0111i\xEAn n\xE0o \u0111\xF3 \u0111\xE3 t\u1EA1o ra thu\u1ED1c bi\u1EBFn
    ng\u01B0\u1EDDi kh\xE1c th\xE0nh zombie, xong th\u1EA3 \u0111\xE1m qu\xE1i v\u1EADt
    \u1EA5y \u0111\u1EA7y \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng. Qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i bu\u1ED9c ph\u1EA3i
    th\u1EA3 bom \u0111\u1EC3 d\u1ECDn d\u1EB9p nh\u01B0ng qu\u1EA3 bom kh\xF4ng
    n\u1ED5. May m\u1EAFn sao m\xECnh ch\xF4m \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c m\u1ED9t kh\u1EA9u
    bazooka tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i r\xFAt lui. M\u1EA5y ng\xE0y
    nay c\u1EE9 th\u1EA5y m\u1ED9t t\xEAn to con cao h\u01A1n c\u1EA3 xe bu\xFDt
    \u0111i l\xF9ng s\u1EE5c kh\u1EAFp n\u01A1i, c\xF3 l\u1EBD m\xECnh n\xEAn d\xF9ng
    kh\u1EA9u bazoka \u0111\u1EC3 gi\u1EBFt h\u1EAFn. M\xECnh c\u1EA5t \u1EDF s\xE2n
    sau nh\xE0 m\xECnh, ch\u1EAFc kh\xF4ng ai nh\xECn th\u1EA5y \u0111\xE2u."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
